This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://fhir.nmdp.org/ig/matchsync/ValueSet/nmdp-rh-status-codes
  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://loinc.org/vs/LL360-9

name: MSRhVS
title: MatchSync Rh Value Sets
description: MatchSync codes for blood Rh. Combines NMDP and LOINC code
